	* interfaces/C/: ppl_c.cc (1.22), ppl_c.h (1.20): All the
	*_and_minimize functions return a positive integer if the reulting
	polyhedron is non-empty; they return 0 if it is empty (and, as
	usual, return a negative number if an error occurred).

