	* tests/: Makefile.am, relations9.cc (strict.[2,1]): Test
	relations9 calls method PolyBase::relation_with(c) when *this is a
	necessarily closed polyhedron and c is a strict inequality.

2002-03-26 Tuesday 13:58  Enea Zaffanella <zaffanella@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/: GenSys.cc, PolyBase.cc (strict.[11,30]): Methods
	PolyBase::relation_with(c) and GenSys::relation_with(c) modified to
	work as expected when *this.topology() == NECESSARILY_CLOSED and
	the c.type() == STRICT_INEQUALITY.

