2002-03-13 Wednesday 20:16  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* interfaces/Prolog/ppl_prolog.outlines.hh (1.20),
	interfaces/Prolog/GNU/ppl_gprolog.pl (1.2),
