2002-03-12 Tuesday 11:44  Enea Zaffanella <zaffanella@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/: Constraint.defs.hh (1.44), Generator.defs.hh (1.48),
	Generator.inlines.hh (1.21): The method Constraint::type() and the
	corresponding enum Constraint::Type are now public.  Added new
	public type tests to Generator, is_ray() and is_vertex(); also, the
	existing method is_line() is now public.

2002-03-12 Tuesday 11:23  Enea Zaffanella <zaffanella@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/: Generator.cc (1.22), Generator.defs.hh (1.47),
	Generator.inlines.hh (1.20): We were still throwing an exception
	from the inlined method divisor(); added a non-inline function for
	that purpose.

