	std::invalid_argument(...).

2001-10-17 Wednesday 11:03  Elisa Ricci <ericci@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/Generator.inlines.hh (1.5): Used the concatenation of two
	strings in the argument of std::invalid_argument(...).

